column5: yeah ive tried the taping method, arctic buffalos 1mm single flares, weights, everything. idk why but my ears just like to flare up and have problems

like when they cut out a bit of ur earlobe out to make the hole bigger. im @ 1" but i wanna get them scalpelled to 1 1/4" or 1 1/2"!! ive been trying to stretch them myself for years but they never seem to be able to go past 1",, like everytime i try i just have problems
